<HEADLINE>
O.J. JERSEY FLAP SHOWS NO SIGN OF GOING AWAY
</HEADLINE>
 (EDS, resending with correct slug line) 
(Dennis McCarthy is a columnist for the Los Angeles Daily News) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DENNIS McCARTHY  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ If anyone thinks the name O.J. Simpson doesn't
