inspectors, fudged, lied, and reverted to its previous
circumlocutions.
</P>
<P>
   _ Accuse the investigator of framing you. Clinton's defenders
accuse Starr's prosecutors of pressuring witnesses such as Betty
Currie and Susan McDougal to testify falsely against Clinton. Iraq
