<HEADLINE>
ASIAN FLU KILLS OFF 48,000 JOBS AT BOEING  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Seattle, Washington-State Editors)   (This ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent newspaper in
London.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from New York Times
Syndicate sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (ATTN. EDITORS: FOR THOSE DESIRING A SHORTER VERSION, THIS ARTICLE
STANDS IN 475 WORDS. TOTAL UNCUT VERSION IS 975 WORDS.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``a'' domestic/general news and ``f'' financial news files.)  
  
 By MICHAEL HARRISON  
 c.1998 The Independent, London  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
