<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-03 16:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1650 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JOHNSON-COLUMN-TEX     12-03 0787
