Inc. chief executive Russell Erxleben were unsuccessful recently in
their battle to keep correspondence between attorneys and Erxleben
privileged. (Tyson, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   PEAK-INTL-ACQUISITION _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Austin's Peak
International Ltd. fired its chief executive recently, two weeks
after reporting that it was the target of a possible acquisition.
MOVED.
