   AUS-BUSH-ISRAEL _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Gov. George W. Bush talks to
reporters about his trip to Israel at a morning briefing. (Herman,
Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   CODIS _ DNA, the genetic fingerprint that scientists call the
building block of life, is rapidly becoming the stumbling block of
the violent criminal. Major advances in the forensic analysis of
DNA are culminating with in the linkage of 40 now-separate state
databases containing thousands of DNA samples from known criminals
and criminal investigations, all under the administration of the
FBI. It's the Combined DNA Index System. (Warner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
