second look. The all-new Alero has style, it has content, it has
value, and it's going after the big guns in the midsize market _
notably Honda Accord. The only thing it doesn't have is a name.
Alero. What's an Alero? Tell people you're driving an Alero, and
they'll say, ``Huh?'' By BOB GOLFEN. Story moved in the ``L``
category. EMBARGOED FOR SATURDAY, DEC. 5. &QL; 
