-- Dick Bavetta, one of the best-known referees in the NBA, can't
wait to get back to his job. ``My body is crying out to me,
'Bavetta, what are doing speaking at a grammar school?' `` he says.
`` 'You should be in the Meadowlands.' It's just because I love
this more than anything. We'll get back.'' (G. Paul Burnett/New
York Times Photo)
