the last two weeks, seven Israeli soldiers were killed in the
region by the Iranian-backed Hezbollah guerrillas. The spate of
funerals sparked anew what has been a cyclical re-examination of
the 20-year-old Israeli occupation of the Israeli ``security
strip'' along the Israeli-Lebanese border. (Rina Castelnuovo/New
York Times Photo)
