-- Drs. Frances and Barbara Rockett in the operating room at
Newton-Wellesley Hospital. The husband and wife team have been
working together as brain surgeons for 30 years. (Tom Herde/Boston
Globe Photo)*LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT5) NEW YORK -- Dec. 3, 1998 -- NY-CHRISTMAS-WINDOWS, 12-03
-- Crowds pass the Christmas diplay at Saks Fifth Avenue.
Department store windows at Christmas time are a ritual as integral
to the season in New York City as snarls of traffic near
Rockefeller Center. But what amounts to a moment's thrill for those
who pass by the windows is the result of months and months of hard
work and planning. (Nicole Bengiveno/New York Times Photo)*LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT4) NEW YORK -- Dec. 3, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN., DEC. 6 --
CANBY-THEATER-2, 12-03 -- Thusitha Jayasundera, left, and Dan Milne
