pulpy parody of puppy love and American culture, the Off Off
Broadway troupe took the leap to their first open-ended commercial
run. (Sara Krulwich/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) NEW YORK -- Dec. 3, 1998 -- ADV. FOR SUN., DEC. 6 --
DUET-THEATER-1, 12-03 -- Members of the Adobe Theater Company
